六</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;font-size: 20px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">章</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学历证书</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:Verdana;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第十</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">五</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Verdana;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">条</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学生在学校规定的年限内，修完教育教学计划规定内容，德、智、体达到毕业要求，由学校颁发</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">黑龙江八一农垦</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Verdana;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大学</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本科</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Verdana;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">毕业证书</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Verdana;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">符合学士学位授予规定的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，颁发普通高等教育本科毕业生学士学位证书</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Verdana;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;text-align:center;line-height:27px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;font-size: 20px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">七</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;font-size: 20px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">章